1. Ove godine smo imali dosta *pljački* u gradu. (This year we had a lot of robberies in the city.)
2. Nije mi jasno kako možeš da podržavaš *pljačke* takvih razmera. (I don't understand how you can support such large-scale robberies.)
3. Policija je uspela da uhvati osumnjičene za *pljačku* banke. (The police managed to catch the suspects for the bank robbery.)
4. Ovaj grad je poznat po čestim *pljačkama* prodavnica. (This city is known for frequent shoplifting.)
5. Njegova firma je optužena za organizovanu *pljačku* državne imovine. (His company is accused of organized theft of state property.)
6. Često se dešava da nevine osobe budu optužene za *pljačku* zbog grešaka u istrazi. (It often happens that innocent people are accused of theft due to investigation errors.)
7. Zbog *pljačke* zlatare je uhapšen njen vlasnik. (The owner of the jewelry store was arrested for the theft.)
8. Prošle nedelje je došlo do *pljačke* pošte u mom kraju. (Last week there was a robbery at the post office in my neighborhood.)
9. Sve više ljudi se odlučuje za *pljačku* kao način za brzu zaradu novca. (More and more people are opting for theft as a way to quickly make money.)
10. Ovaj deo grada je poznat kao centar *pljački* automobila. (This part of the city is known as the center of car theft.)